snippet.title: Ragnarok Online Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.ragnarokeurope.com

Ragnarök Online is known as a reference on the Manga Style MMORPG market. All current MMO have in some forms a bit of Ragnarok DNA. As the game has been regularly updated in terms of content and features, it's one of the biggest MMO on the planet. Thanks to this the retention is impressive and all over the world the game keeps attracting many new players. The Brand is very strong.
